customDashboardUrl.description:
Custom dashboard url that is going to be used in the notification. If not specified it is going to be deduced based on the context. Allowed placeholders are:
{workspaceId}
{dashboardId}
{automationId}
{asOfDate}

notificationSource.description:
Human-readable description of the source of the notification. If specified, this propertywill be included in the notifications to this channel.Allowed placeholders are:
{{workspaceId}}
{{workspaceName}}
{{workspaceDescription}}
{{dashboardId}}
{{dashboardName}}
